    <item>
      <title>由于奖金消失，亚洲顶级银行家的薪酬降至 100 万美元以下</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/top-banker-pay-sinks-below-1-million-in-asia-as-bonuses-vanish</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，亚洲华尔街公司大多数高级投资银行家的薪酬降至近二十年来的最低水平，原因是中国和香港的交易匮乏对该行业造成了打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/top-banker-pay-sinks-below-1-million-in-asia-as-bonuses-vanish</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 01:15:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
